# --- code-noobs Ghost recovery (docs/code-noobs branch) ---
# Recovered Ghost JSON exports carry LIVE secrets: RSA members_private_key,
# admin/content api_keys, session secrets, the "SellMore!" site password,
# Slack + Zapier webhooks, owner bcrypt hash. Never commit the raw dump.
.scratch/code-noobs/*.ghost.json
wiki/docs/code-noobs-archive/*.ghost.json
**/ghost-export*.json
